node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by KTBTv™ | Bass Fishing on August 29, 2021 tagging @noahpescitelli, and @lews_fishing. May be an image of text that says 'THANKYOU FOR THE SUPPORT'.

node.text:
All I can say is THANK YOU – to my team, family, and wonderful supporters who have made this dream a reality. I have been patiently waiting for nearly a decade to drop my own combos. I could not be more proud to partner with @lews_fishing. Although we are currently sold out, there will be more combos COMING SOON.
-
For those who purchased a combo, please expect shipment in the next 30 days. Our team is working hard to quality check product and reply to your emails. We appreciate your patience! Thank you all again!
-
#TeamKTBTv #LewsFishing #KickinTheirBassTv #BigBassEnergy
